{"tid":2365191,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"我想創業賣酒，但係咪要識飲酒阿？","createTime":"2021-01-13T14:12:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T06:13:04.000Z","uid":294317,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a21613dfc881c6960f0ac428bcd0365b668b7d2c","tid":2365191,"uid":294317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:12:02.000Z","msg":"小弟係賣開其他產品既，但想賣威士忌之類既產品，真心有時係到諗，我賣產品都未必會樣樣試過曬，但賣酒好似要成日試，但小弟酒量差...........但入左幾萬貨，我仲諗繼唔繼續落去，定我溫d書，等威士忌知識多d先呢？<br />\n<br />\n有冇賣過酒既人可以建議下我"},{"pid":"c72261db52abb10be7d3cf53000fcd95f3c1b8ec","tid":2365191,"uid":83920,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:14:31.000Z","msg":"你去人地鋪頭買酒，<br />\n個staff問咩都唔識，你會唔會有信心買"},{"pid":"4eb11a6c9d417fe871d8674806ecd17f3088180a","tid":2365191,"uid":368729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c72261db52abb10be7d3cf53000fcd95f3c1b8ec","tid":2365191,"uid":83920,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:14:31.000Z","msg":"你去人地鋪頭買酒，<br />\n個staff問咩都唔識，你會唔會有信心買"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:19:02.000Z","msg":"唔應該咁講，好多都係背吓書，d客問得既佢都吹到出黎"},{"pid":"b99aee4c1457ea0e88b5322787bfb3c124bf2cd4","tid":2365191,"uid":294317,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c72261db52abb10be7d3cf53000fcd95f3c1b8ec","tid":2365191,"uid":83920,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:14:31.000Z","msg":"你去人地鋪頭買酒，<br />\n個staff問咩都唔識，你會唔會有信心買"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:20:01.000Z","msg":"有道理🤔🤔🤔但你賣零食都唔駛每款試過，一理馬國名喎"},{"pid":"990a59778c66e2156798083a89d2bf3e63519825","tid":2365191,"uid":294317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4eb11a6c9d417fe871d8674806ecd17f3088180a","tid":2365191,"uid":368729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c72261db52abb10be7d3cf53000fcd95f3c1b8ec","tid":2365191,"uid":83920,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:14:31.000Z","msg":"你去人地鋪頭買酒，<br />\n個staff問咩都唔識，你會唔會有信心買"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-1